The paper deals with underwater image enhancement, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The authors also mention the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the construction of a benchmark dataset (cs.MM) and the evaluation of algorithms (cs.GR).
